date_of_review: Reviewed in the United States on October 3, 2020
review_content: I absolutely did not expect this to be the case with snacks from such a big name, but yeah, the expiration dates are horrible on this product. Truth be told, things like this are usually good after the expiration for a bit, so I didn't have a problem seeing that at first.
